original_title: Θου-Βου Φαλακρός Πράκτωρ, Επιχείρηση: Γης Μαδιάμ
overview: Thou-Vou and his new partner, MAP31, accept three imaginary tasks from a cunning director who is only interested in filming the unsuspecting duo for his upcoming movie feature. Will the agents manage to squeeze success out of failure?
title: The Baldheaded Agent and the Land of Destruction Mission
